label: A_mC4_15_e-001
title: $\beta$-Ga Structure ({\em Obsolete})
comments: This was proposed as a metastable structure of gallium, visible for short times at atomospheric pressure.  The true structure is isostructural with \href{current_web_home_dir/A_tI2_139_a-001}{indium ($A6$)}, and stablized under pressure.
